---
---

<section class="section-pain" aria-labelledby="pain-h2">
  <div class="pain-inner">
    <span class="pill pill-amber story-element" data-story-delay="0">A realidade hoje</span>
    <h2 class="pain-h2 story-element" id="pain-h2" data-story-delay="1">
      A planilha não avisa<br />quem você está esquecendo.
    </h2>
    <p class="pain-sub story-element" data-story-delay="2">
      E o médico que você não visitou há 45 dias já está prescrevendo o concorrente.
    </p>

    <div class="pain-grid">
      <article class="pain-card story-element" data-story-delay="2">
        <div class="pain-num red" data-counter="34" data-suffix="%" aria-label="34%">0%</div>
        <h3 class="pain-card-title">dos seus médicos estratégicos</h3>
        <p class="pain-card-text">ficam sem visita por mais de 60 dias sem que você perceba.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="pain-card story-element" data-story-delay="3">
        <div class="pain-num amber" data-counter="2" data-suffix="h" aria-label="2 horas">0h</div>
        <h3 class="pain-card-title">por dia em relatórios</h3>
        <p class="pain-card-text">é o tempo médio que propagandistas gastam digitando visitas que poderiam ter sido faladas.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="pain-card story-element" data-story-delay="4">
        <div class="pain-num red">
          <span class="pain-rs">R$ </span>
          <span data-counter="0" data-suffix="" aria-label="R$ 0">0</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="pain-card-title">de comissão por falta de follow-up</h3>
        <p class="pain-card-text">follow-ups perdidos = prescrições perdidas = comissão que ficou na mesa.</p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <blockquote class="pain-quote story-element" data-story-delay="2">
      <p class="pain-quote-text">
        Eu tinha uma planilha com 280 médicos. Mas nunca sabia quem estava esperando minha visita há mais tempo.
      </p>
      <footer class="pain-quote-attr">— Relato de propagandista com 6 anos de experiência</footer>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-pain {
    min-height: 100vh;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 100px clamp(24px, 5vw, 80px);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-pain::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30%;
    left: -10%;
    width: 60%;
    height: 80%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .pain-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .pain-h2 {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    line-height: 1.0;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 24px;
  }

  .pain-sub {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--color-stone-500);
    margin-top: 20px;
    max-width: 700px;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 64px;
  }

  .pain-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-amber) 40%, transparent);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 36px;
    transition: border-color 250ms, transform 250ms, box-shadow 250ms;
  }

  .pain-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-amber);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -15px rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.25);
  }

  .pain-num {
    font-size: clamp(48px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
  }

  .pain-num.red { color: var(--color-red); }
  .pain-num.amber { color: var(--color-amber); }
  .pain-rs { font-size: 0.65em; font-weight: 600; }

  .pain-card-title {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .pain-card-text {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-stone-500);
    margin-top: 8px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pain-quote {
    margin-top: 64px;
    max-width: 760px;
    position: relative;
    padding-top: 40px;
  }

  .pain-quote::before {
    content: "\201C";
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    left: -8px;
    font-size: 120px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-amber) 40%, transparent);
    font-family: Georgia, serif;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .pain-quote-text {
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.5vw, 30px);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-stone-600);
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .pain-quote-attr {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .pain-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .pain-card { padding: 28px; }
  }
</style>
